             <td class="statText" colspan="2">
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td class="statText" colspan="2">
              <h3>
               Notes
              </h3>
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
              The returned value must be accurate to within a relative or absolute value of 1E-9.
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td class="statText" colspan="2">
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td class="statText" colspan="2">
              <h3>
               Constraints
              </h3>
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
              <b>
               data
              </b>
              will contain between 6 and 50 elements inclusive.
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
              Each element of
              <b>
               data
              </b>
              will be between 10.0 and 100.0 inclusive.
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td class="statText" colspan="2">
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td class="statText" colspan="2">
              <h3>
               Examples
              </h3>
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" nowrap="true">
              0)
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td class="statText">
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
              <table>
               <tr>
                <td class="statText">
                 <table>
                  <tr>
                   <td class="statText">
                    <pre>{10,10,10,10,10,10}</pre>
                   </td>
                  </tr>
                 </table>
                </td>
               </tr>
               <tr>
                <td class="statText">
                 <pre>Returns: 0.0</pre>
                </td>
               </tr>
               <tr>
                <td class="statText">
                 <table>
                  <tr>
                   <td class="statText" colspan="2">
                    A weighting of .2,.2,.2,.2,.2 will exactly predict the only past price that
   had 5 predecessors.
                   </td>
                  </tr>
                 </table>
                </td>
               </tr>
              </table>
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" nowrap="true">
              1)
             </td>
